parameters.name: st_met
parameters.description: The start MET time of the coarse-fine energy sweep used to determine the solar wind parameters.

parameters.name: sp_met
parameters.description: The stop MET time of the coarse-fine energy sweep used to determine the solar wind parameters.

parameters.name: n
parameters.description: Tolar wind proton density in units of cm^-3.

parameters.name: v
parameters.description: The solar wind proton speed in units of km/s.

parameters.name: t
parameters.description: The solar wind proton temperature in units of K.

parameters.name: pdyn
parameters.description: The solar wind proton dynamic pressure in units of nPa.

parameters.name: pth
parameters.description: The solar wind thermal dynamic pressure in units of pPa.

parameters.name: NH_HGI_D_X
parameters.description: The x component of the center of the spacecraft position in HGI coordinates in units of AU.

parameters.name: NH_HGI_D_Y
parameters.description: The y component of the center of the NH spacecraft position in HGI coordinates in units of AU.

parameters.name: NH_HGI_D_Z
parameters.description: The z component of the center of the spacecraft position in HGI coordinates in units of AU.

parameters.name: NH_HGI_D_R
parameters.description: The distance to the center of the NH spacecraft position from the center of the HGI coordinate system (Sun) in units of AU.

parameters.name: NH_HGI_D_LAT
parameters.description: The latitude of the center of the NH spacecraft position in HGI coordinates in degrees.

parameters.name: NH_HGI_D_LON
parameters.description: The longitude of the center of the NH spacecraft position in HGI coordinates in degrees.

parameters.name: NH_HAE_J2000_D_X
parameters.description: The x component of the center of the spacecraft position in HAE coordinates in units of AU.

parameters.name: NH_HAE_J2000_D_Y
parameters.description: The y component of the center of the spacecraft position in HAE coordinates in units of AU.

parameters.name: NH_HAE_J2000_D_Z
parameters.description: The y component of the center of the spacecraft position in HAE coordinates in units of AU.

parameters.name: NH_HAE_J2000_D_LAT
parameters.description: The latitude of the center of the spacecraft position in HAE coordinates in units of degrees.

parameters.name: NH_HAE_J2000_D_LON
parameters.description: The longitude of the center of the spacecraft position in HAE coordinates in units of degrees.

parameters.description: The y component of the center of the spacecraft position in HG coordinates in units of AU.

parameters.name: NH_HG_D_LAT
